Out of the whirling sandstorm rise the Dervish to offer their blood for the battle ahead. They are bound to the very storm from which they draw their power and thus must give of themselves to the sands.

In exchange for great freedom of movement and the ability to utilize two weapons, they give up the ability to wear certain armors and they must always be at the front of battle.

Their home is located among the deserts of Snow's realm.
